726753f-a.text:
Grand Avenue, south side between Goldsmith and Van Loon Streets, showing two views of the Goldsmith house. Eliza F. Leverich, a daughter of Col. Edward Leverich who died in 1833, married the Rev. John Goldsmith. Mrs. Goldsmith was the owner in 1873 and J.H. Prall in 1891.
1922
View 2:June 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
